{
  "stem": "4513.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, hey, what can they do?' So I think-- and what happened was at some point, we finished-- we finished that training.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then once you finish all your 13 weeks, you have to sit around waiting on your assignment.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had applied for ASTP, which was a college program to go back to school, which they were sending a lot of kids back.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'd also applied for OCS-- officers training.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They all told me I was a little bit young for-- for officer training, but they would see what they could do.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had scored very well in all my issues and they said they were gonna try to get me in there with my non-commissioned officers.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What happened was I went to Richmond on a three-day pass.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Coming back at the end of the three-day pass, I stepped back to let a black woman on in front of me who had groceries, and I told her to get on the bus in front of me.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this white soldier screamed, don't let that black bitch on in front of you!",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I hit him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we started-- a mini riot occurred.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The guys turned over the bus and all the black soldiers took the square in Richmond for about three or four hours until the MPs came with [INAUDIBLE] 50 caliber machine guns and told us to get on the buses and go back to camp.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And going back, they said, we're not gonna tell anybody what happened here.' And I said, fine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They quarantined us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They put MPs around our barracks, and we couldn't come out except under escort.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
